summary: This is an email dated October 26, 2021, from an individual named Mina, transmitting new serials and multiple attachments related to the Epstein case. The attachments include documents about a call, evidence collection, interviews, materials from the Palm Beach Police Department, trial expense reimbursements, subpoenas, property receipts, trash pulls, and accusations of rape and human trafficking.
